    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Fine powders of various materials used to treat or protect the surface of a drawing or of parchment, or to transfer a design through a pricked drawing.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
